com.apriori.apt.reflect

Class ArField

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.apriori.apt.reflect.ArField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ArAnnotatedElement, ArMember

    public class ArField
extends java.lang.Object
    A field. This is analogous to Field, except that it represents fields in Java source (during annotation processing) vs. representing fields of runtime types.
    See Also:
    Field
